PROJECT NAME

OTPVerify Pro


---

PROJECT SUMMARY

Build a complete SaaS platform where users can register, fund wallets, purchase digital services, manage orders, earn referral commissions, contact support, and withdraw unused wallet balances back to their verified bank accounts.

The system must support:

User accounts

Wallet system

Deposits

Withdrawals

Orders

Refunds

Referrals

Notifications

KYC verification

Admin management

Reporting and analytics


The platform must be mobile-first and production-ready.


