BUSINESS RULES

Every user gets a wallet.

Failed orders are refunded automatically.

Users can withdraw unused wallet funds.

KYC is required before withdrawals.

Referral commissions are automated.

All transactions are permanently logged.

Admin actions are audited.

Email and in-app notifications are mandatory.



---

Goal: Build a production-ready fintech-style SaaS platform with wallet funding, withdrawals, referrals, support, analytics, and complete user/admin management.